skills.name: Ties of the Wind
skills.description: [SP: 18][CD: 0s] Fires compressed air projectiles in a straight trajectory, dealing 110% ATK of Physical DMG to all enemies hit. Caster gains 10 SP if the projectile hits at least 1 bleeding enemy.
